---
// Founders — message from the founders section
---

<section class="founders section">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">A Message From the Founders</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading">The People Behind Obvius</h2>
    <div class="founders__grid">

      <!-- Tolu Mebaanne -->
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-card__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/founders/Toluwalase_Mebaanne.jpeg"
            alt="Tolu Mebaanne, Co-Founder of Obvius Digital"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="founder-card__name">Tolu Mebaanne</h3>
        <span class="founder-card__title">Co-Founder / Media Production</span>
        <p class="founder-card__message">
          [PLACEHOLDER] Tolu's message from the founders — share what drives you, what you believe about small business marketing, and why you built Obvius the way you did.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-card__socials">
          <a href="[PLACEHOLDER_INSTAGRAM_TOLU]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Tolu on Instagram">Instagram</a>
          <a href="[PLACEHOLDER_LINKEDIN_TOLU]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Tolu on LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kayla Sippel -->
      <div class="founder-card">
        <div class="founder-card__photo">
          <img
            src="/images/founders/Kayla_Sippel.jpeg"
            alt="Kayla Sippel, Co-Founder of Obvius Digital"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="founder-card__name">Kayla Sippel</h3>
        <span class="founder-card__title">Co-Founder / Communications &amp; Strategy</span>
        <p class="founder-card__message">
          [PLACEHOLDER] Kayla's message from the founders — share what makes Obvius different from a communications and strategy perspective, and what you bring to every client relationship.
        </p>
        <div class="founder-card__socials">
          <a href="[PLACEHOLDER_INSTAGRAM_KAYLA]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Kayla on Instagram">Instagram</a>
          <a href="[PLACEHOLDER_LINKEDIN_KAYLA]" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Kayla on LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
